<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ca">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Formulari d'Accessibilitat Post-ruta</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      height: 100vh;
      background-color: #73edff !important;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      position: relative;
      color: #000078;
    }

    .container {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
      overflow-y: auto;
      max-height: 90vh;
    }

    h1, h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    p {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    textarea, input[type="number"] {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 8px;
      margin-top: 5px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 4px;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    button {
      margin-top: 20px;
      background-color: #000078;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: #000050;
    }

    .logo {
      position: absolute;
      top: 20px;
      right: 20px;
      width: 100px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <img src="/logo.png" alt="Logo" class="logo">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Formulari sobre accessibilitat (Post-ruta)</h1>
    <form method="POST" action="/post_submit">
      <input type="hidden" name="idAnswer" value="<%= idAnswer %>" />

      <h3>Preguntes post-ruta:</h3>

      <p>Has pogut transitar sense dificultats durant tota la ruta?</p>
      <label><input type="radio" name="transitabilitat" value="Sí" required> Sí</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="transitabilitat" value="No"> No</label>

      <p>L’amplada de les voreres era suficient per moure’t amb facilitat?</p>
      <label><input type="radio" name="amplada_voreres" value="Sí" required> Sí</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="amplada_voreres" value="No"> No</label>

      <p>Si la resposta és no, indica quin o quins carrers has trobat dificultats:</p>
      <textarea name="carrers_dificultats" rows="3"></textarea>

      <p>Has trobat obstacles (mobiliari urbà, arbres, pots, etc.) que impedeixen el pas?</p>
      <label><input type="radio" name="obstacles" value="Sí" required> Sí</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="obstacles" value="No"> No</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="obstacles" value="Alguns"> Alguns</label>

      <p>Has trobat llocs per descansar al llarg de la ruta?</p>
      <label><input type="radio" name="descans" value="Sí" required> Sí</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="descans" value="No"> No</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="descans" value="No ho necessitava"> No ho necessitava</label>

      <p>Els passos de vianants eren accessibles i identificables?</p>
      <label><input type="radio" name="passos_accessibles" value="Sí" required> Sí</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="passos_accessibles" value="No"> No</label>

      <p>T’has sentit segur/a durant la ruta?</p>
      <label><input type="radio" name="seguretat" value="Sí" required> Sí</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="seguretat" value="No"> No</label>

      <p>Quin % d’accessibilitat li donaries a la ruta?</p>
      <input type="number" name="percentatge_accessibilitat" min="0" max="100" required>

      <p>Comentaris o suggeriments per millorar la ruta:</p>
      <textarea name="comentaris" rows="4"></textarea>

      <button type="submit">Enviar</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
